## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="2df9c-157"><xref:System.Net.Http.HttpClient> 被要具現化一次和重複使用的應用程式生命週期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2df9c-157"><xref:System.Net.Http.HttpClient> is intended to be instantiated once and re-used throughout the life of an application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2df9c-158">每個要求的 HttpClient 類別具現化會耗盡可用在沈重負載下的通訊端數目。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2df9c-158">Instantiating an HttpClient class for every request will exhaust the number of sockets available under heavy loads.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2df9c-159">這會導致 SocketException 錯誤。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2df9c-159">This will result in SocketException errors.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2df9c-160">以下是正確地使用 HttpClient 範例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2df9c-160">Below is an example using HttpClient correctly.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
public class GoodController : ApiController  
{  
    // OK  
    private static readonly HttpClient HttpClient;  
  
    static GoodController()  
    {  
        HttpClient = new HttpClient();  
    }  
}  
  
```
